data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom gem offers 2,541 sq ft of pure comfort and elegance. Nestled on a cul-de-sac, it boasts a spacious lot, complete with a 2-car garage, a refreshing pool, and a backyard that provides endless possibilities. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a generous living area that flows seamlessly into an updated kitchen and family room. The kitchen features a massive island, perfect for hosting gatherings and creating culinary delights. Venturing further, to the left, you'll discover three well-appointed bedrooms. Down the hallway awaits the impressive master suite, complete with its own private bathroom.    Returning to the front of the home, past the kitchen, you'll find an expansive covered lanai that leads to a screened-in pool and spa tub—a true oasis for relaxation and entertainment. Beyond the pool area lies a sprawling backyard, providing ample space for outdoor activities and your own private retreat.    This home offers more than just a place to live; it offers a lifestyle. With a new roof (just 4 years old) and a well-maintained AC system (only 8 years old) as well a water filtration system, you can move in with peace of mind.     Located in a prime location, this residence is a rare find in today's market. Opportunities like this don't come along often, so don't hesitate! Contact us today to schedule a viewing and secure your piece of paradise!!
